Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: El Salvador elections
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wv6s
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Apr 1982
Big turnout for El Salvador elections which vote in extreme right-wingers. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.